Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.86,0:03:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,危險  鶇小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.53,0:04:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.45,0:04:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,綾崎颯！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:12.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Hah, serves you right!\N\N{\r}\N哼  活該！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.88,0:04:18.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Let's get away with the money.\N\N{\r}\N我們抓緊拿錢跑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.27,0:04:20.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈亞太！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.58,0:04:22.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯  振作點！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.27,0:04:28.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…我還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.98,0:04:30.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:32.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看到你被刺中了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.89,0:04:33.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還以為…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.99,0:04:35.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看上去哪裡都沒有受傷呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.06,0:04:41.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…真的沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.61,0:04:44.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.39,0:04:47.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.64,0:04:57.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.09,0:05:02.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}What's this!?\N\N{\r}\N這是什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.56,0:05:17.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑椿…把黑椿給我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.83,0:05:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.03,0:05:20.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑椿是…？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.37,0:05:22.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑椿…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.36,0:05:25.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Die, you monster!\N\N{\r}\N去死吧  怪物！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Go to hell!\N\N{\r}\N下地獄吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,泉  沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:38.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.17,0:05:43.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  先逃離這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:45.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.66,0:05:46.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯也快點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒關係  你們請先走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.48,0:05:53.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你就是綾崎颯嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.86,0:06:06.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑椿在你手裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:10.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,來  把它給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:14.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快把黑椿給我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.37,0:06:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,照做的話  就把你重要的公主還給你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.35,0:06:21.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯——！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.06,0:06:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這種事  我有些話想和你說
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.86,0:06:29.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼…「這種事」？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:33.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…你這說法算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:36.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的狀況說成是「這種事」  你是怎麼想的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你聽到我說了嗎  小颯！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:39.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:43.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,閒聊什麼的  等你把黑椿給我之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:49.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.46,0:06:51.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把小凪…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.84,0:06:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把小凪放開！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.22,0:07:06.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,什  什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.18,0:07:16.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Hey! Let's get out of here!\N\N{\r}\N嘿！我們趁機離開這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.93,0:07:27.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我的錢…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.84,0:07:31.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把我的錢還給我——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.83,0:07:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你——！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:38.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要對我母親出手！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.59,0:07:43.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多莉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.85,0:07:46.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,離開聖域太長時間了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.97,0:07:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把黑椿…黑…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.77,0:07:53.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行了  身體要堅持不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.99,0:07:55.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,暫時先回聖域吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.72,0:07:59.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把…黑…椿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑椿…我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多莉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.68,0:08:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多莉…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉了  現在只能…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.63,0:08:20.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,黑…椿…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不能讓你們逃走…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.15,0:08:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手——！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,鶇  你也趕快撤離這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:37.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.12,0:08:59.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.58,0:09:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.99,0:09:09.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,難道是為剛才的事生氣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.99,0:09:11.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:14.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才大發雷霆的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:20.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是那件事的話…我會道歉的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.44,0:09:24.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  不要用這種態度…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:32.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.99,0:09:33.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.31,0:09:37.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你要去哪裡  我話還沒說完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:39.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去哪裡和你沒有關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有關係？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.94,0:09:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是我的管家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.97,0:09:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「管家」…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:52.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你從剛才開始怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.09,0:09:56.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你不是和我約好了嗎  要在危難的時候拯救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.09,0:09:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說「這是管家的使命」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.87,0:10:02.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不再做管家了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:07.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.81,0:10:10.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.48,0:10:18.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小…颯…？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.48,0:10:46.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我說…小凪？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.55,0:11:19.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全——沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.41,0:11:21.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算沒有小颯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.07,0:11:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也完全沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:25.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.92,0:11:29.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,完全  沒問題！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明顯是逞強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.82,0:11:36.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在逞強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.04,0:11:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是在逞強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.70,0:11:42.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之  好不容易來一趟拉斯維加斯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:45.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們去觀光吧  觀光
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.76,0:12:02.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你們在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.93,0:12:07.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  是老師啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:08.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您怎麼會在這裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.06,0:12:11.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是雪路請我過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.64,0:12:15.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐？說起來這車子是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.32,0:12:17.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來似乎很高檔  這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.42,0:12:21.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  這個？雪路她啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:25.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,對啊  我賺了一大筆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:26.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我之後會付錢的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.05,0:12:30.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你先用你的存款幫我買輛最好的車吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.25,0:12:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,於是  我就買了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.69,0:12:38.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說來  你們知道雪路人在哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天開始就不接電話了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,老師  你這車子好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.44,0:12:47.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  是嗎  你也這麼覺得是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:52.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們去兜兜風吧？到51區附近去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.94,0:12:57.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那個…小凪？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.98,0:13:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找一下姐姐  小颯的事情就麻煩瑪莉亞小姐了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.74,0:13:07.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}老師老師  真的可以帶我們到51區嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.35,0:13:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.12,0:13:09.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}那裡可是很了不起的地區啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:10.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.97,0:13:07.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這種情況下我們也很難專心地找他們
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.57,0:13:09.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.26,0:13:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那小凪就交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.03,0:13:15.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  那就麻煩您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:16.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.39,0:13:19.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:32.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  你是西澤小姐嗎  請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.16,0:13:37.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,說起來  三千院
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.84,0:13:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你跟綾崎他怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.56,0:13:43.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我也不可能一直都跟小颯他在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.85,0:13:46.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  但之前一直都在一起的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:48.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是你的管家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:56.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦  怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.08,0:14:00.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  對了  有件事我忘記跟小凪你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.26,0:14:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這東西是小颯的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.56,0:14:08.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！你是怎麼把它…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.48,0:14:10.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這是我昨天無意中撿到的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.34,0:14:15.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我無意間走到一邊的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.14,0:14:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,偶然發現了掉在地上的這東西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:26.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是犯人在逃跑的時候運氣不好掉下的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.93,0:14:28.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.28,0:14:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿著這東西那就說明…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.23,0:14:35.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  爆胎了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.20,0:14:36.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦——！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.27,0:14:37.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然是這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.54,0:14:40.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,剎車  剎車啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.31,0:14:44.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  完全剎不了車！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你沒事吧  小凪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.99,0:15:13.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  總算是沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.03,0:15:16.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…大家都平安無事實在是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.84,0:15:19.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  為什麼車子會突然爆胎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.99,0:15:21.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都是因為這懷錶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,這被稱作黑椿的東西  是一塊招來惡運的魔懷錶
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:28.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:32.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不見了  剛剛明明還在手上的懷錶不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,應該是掉到哪裡了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:36.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼辦啊  我把它弄丟了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.07,0:15:39.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那懷錶什麼的就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.65,0:15:42.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是剛剛途中掉下來了  我去找一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.21,0:15:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我都說算了嘛…喂  倉鼠！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.32,0:15:50.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也到路邊攔車叫人去  三千院你先留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.37,0:15:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:58.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  早知就不來拉斯維加斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.18,0:16:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻笨蛋倉鼠  明明就掉在這裡了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.87,0:16:13.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在一切危險中保護好大小姐  是我作為管家的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.89,0:16:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  明明都說過那樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:23.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你不在身邊  我一個人也沒問題的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.64,0:16:28.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一個人…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:33.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一個人也能行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.17,0:16:42.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我要死了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:49.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,照這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.44,0:16:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,該有人會從內華達沙漠發現一具身份不明的美少女的屍體了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.30,0:16:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.51,0:17:01.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是小偷嗎  那可是我的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:03.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要隨便拿走啊  你這蠢仙人掌！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.26,0:17:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,還給我  把我的手帕還給我！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.95,0:17:12.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.54,0:17:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,區區仙人掌就想讓我動真格
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.91,0:17:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定會後悔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:23.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好熱！我的手燒傷了！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.87,0:17:27.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我的眼睛  眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.04,0:17:29.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.19,0:17:46.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯——！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.16,0:17:54.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會來了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:57.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小颯已經不是我的管家了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:03.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我來保護  我會來保護大小姐的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.15,0:18:08.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  起床了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:14.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐  您沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.29,0:18:16.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.64,0:18:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請交給我吧  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,請放心  無論是過去還是未來  我都會保護您的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.53,0:18:24.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.23,0:18:27.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再見了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.70,0:18:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:36.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要我不要我不要我不要我不要我不要我不要我不要…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:39.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.70,0:18:43.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我不要這樣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:50.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我什麼都不要了  全都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不會任性了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.77,0:19:00.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會早起的  也會好好到學校上課去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.54,0:19:05.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我會改正我的缺點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.93,0:19:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我決不要…小颯離開我啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.81,0:19:22.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們就去找他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.31,0:19:35.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼就再次見到他  把你的心情傳達給他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.72,0:19:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起去吧  把小颯找回來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.88,0:19:52.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.29,0:20:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  你等我一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.52,0:20:04.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  我叫你等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.20,0:20:09.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  到底是怎麼回事啊  我很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:11.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也是很忙的好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.90,0:20:14.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要拿回那十二億日元啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.47,0:20:16.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那關我什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.48,0:20:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你稍微幫我一下不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.14,0:20:23.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,明明就是從你那裡拿來的叫什麼黑椿的懷錶惹出的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:24.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快幫我  趕快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.99,0:20:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼  我能幫你什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.25,0:20:33.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你！先過來這邊～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.27,0:20:40.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,總之
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.28,0:20:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我捉到了其中一個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.51,0:20:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你這人是有多過分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.93,0:20:49.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,先別說這個了  你至少也是白皇的學生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.59,0:20:51.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,英語總是能說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:53.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你去問他一下錢的下落吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.33,0:20:54.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.67,0:20:57.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,需要嚴刑拷打的話…我可以幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.18,0:20:58.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.79,0:21:02.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.00,0:21:04.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Well...\N\N{\r}\N好吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:09.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}If you don't want to be killed by the gorilla behind me.\N\N{\r}\N要是你不想被後面那隻母猩猩殺掉的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.68,0:21:13.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}I highly suggest you tell us where you're keeping the money.\N\N{\r}\N就告訴我們錢都放在什麼地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.55,0:21:10.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}哎？猩猩？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}剛剛你說了猩猩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.28,0:21:13.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}喂  你是說了「猩猩」這詞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.12,0:21:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你說了吧  「猩猩」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.39,0:21:17.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.84,0:21:21.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我這邊也是很忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.06,0:21:26.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要嘛說要嘛死  你能不能快點選？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.74,0:21:28.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Okay! Okay! Okay! I'll tell you!\N\N{\r}\NOK  OK  OK  我告訴你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.15,0:21:30.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Where's the money?\N\N{\r}\N錢在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.90,0:21:31.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Our boss has it.\N\N{\r}\N我們老大拿走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.65,0:21:36.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}If our team got separated, \Nwe were to meet there to get our share.\N\N{\r}\N\N\N如果大家走散了  我們會另外集中起來再分那筆錢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.45,0:21:37.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}Where exactly?\N\N{\r}\N地點在哪裡？
