Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.39,0:22:00.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰是母猩猩啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:03.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是說了「猩猩」這詞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.47,0:22:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒說
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:06.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,誰說了猩猩誰就是猩猩！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.67,0:22:09.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…哎？
