Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:30.33,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}渴いた心　持て余して
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.46,0:22:33.14,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}展開なら氣分次第
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:36.00,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}剎那へと誘うあなたは
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:40.56,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}戲れの中で　自由すぎるわ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:47.50,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,5000)}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:56.46,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}純真無垢な劍　振り翳す私を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.66,0:23:02.09,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}激しく射拔いて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:02.33,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:04.38,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:07.94,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天使のような　微笑みで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:10.79,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}蜜よりも甘く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:16.32,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}恋の罠　仕掛けてみる（感じて）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:24.52,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“汝、今スグ　罪深キ　愛ノ概念ヲ　悔イ改メヨ”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.63,0:23:27.04,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}清らかに導かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.23,0:23:32.47,EDJ,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}聖なる魂　あなたを抱きしめたい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.34,0:22:27.68,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}Won't you show me all your secrets now?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.77,0:22:30.33,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾澀的心蜷縮在荒漠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.46,0:22:33.14,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}乾澀了它的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.43,0:22:36.00,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}剎那間被誘惑的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.16,0:22:40.56,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}在欺騙的愛中沉淪
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.38,0:22:47.50,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,5000)\an2}Get out……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.89,0:22:56.46,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}希望揮舞純真無邪之劍的你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.66,0:23:02.09,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}盡情地讓疼痛貫穿我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:02.33,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an1}Just say you love me
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.41,0:23:04.38,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}You know I've got a crush on you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.90,0:23:07.94,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}天使般的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.08,0:23:10.79,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}比蜜還甜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.96,0:23:16.32,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}設下愛情的陷阱（感受吧）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:24.52,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}“汝那罪惡的愛情觀　現在立刻悔改吧”
